flowchart LR
  Student[Student browser user] --> Web[React/Vite web client]
  Admin[Admin browser user] --> Web
  Web -->|same-origin fetch| Proxy[Vite dev proxy or production reverse proxy]
  Proxy -->|/auth /student-profile /tutor /admin /usage /webrtc /health| API[NestJS API]
  Web --> Speech[Browser SpeechRecognition API]
  API --> SQLite[(SQLite app.sqlite)]
  API --> BackgroundJobs[In-process background AI worker]
  BackgroundJobs --> SQLite
  BackgroundJobs --> ModelProvider
  API --> TranscriptFiles[Transcript log files]
  API --> ModelProvider[AI model provider facade]
  ModelProvider --> OpenAIResponses[OpenAI Responses API]
  ModelProvider --> OpenAIImages[OpenAI Images API]
  ModelProvider --> OpenAIFiles[OpenAI Files API]
  ModelProvider --> OpenAIVectors[OpenAI Vector Stores]
  API <-->|WebRTC audio/provider data| OpenAIRealtime[OpenAI Realtime API]
  API -. optional .-> STUN[Configured STUN/TURN servers]
